The paper proposes a novel model-based reinforcement learning algorithm that combines policy networks with online planning. This algorithm is evaluated on the MuJoCo benchmarking environments and achieves state-of-the-art performance. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The algorithm also involves optimization problems and neural networks, which are relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
